<typeStatus box="[978,1040,1701,1727]" pageId="50" pageNumber="51">types</typeStatus>
, in particular from coastal biotopes and heathlands (
<bibRefCitation author="Pollet, M. &amp; Grootaert, P." box="[333,610,1737,1764]" pageId="50" pageNumber="51" pagination="859 - 880" refId="ref35039" refString="Pollet, M. &amp; Grootaert, P. (1996) An estimation of the natural value of dune habitats using Empidoidea (Diptera). Biodiversity and Conservation, 5 (7), 859 - 880. https: // doi. org / 10.1007 / BF 00054739" type="journal article" year="1996">Pollet &amp; Grootaert 1996</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
